{"tree":{"type":"node","kind":"SOURCE_FILE","width":28,"children":[{"type":"node","kind":"LET_BINDING","width":28,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"let","width":3},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"IDENT_PATTERN","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"x","width":1}]},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"=","width":1},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":"\n  ","width":3},{"type":"node","kind":"LET_EXPR","width":18,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"let","width":3},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"ERROR","width":4,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"open","width":4}]},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"M","width":1}]},{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"in","width":2},{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":"\n  ","width":3},{"type":"node","kind":"APPLY_EXPR","width":3,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"WHITESPACE","text":" ","width":1},{"type":"node","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"f","width":1}]},{"type":"node","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","width":1,"children":[{"type":"token","kind":"IDENT_EXPR","text":"y","width":1}]}]}]}]}]},"diagnostics":[{"kind":{"id":"E0007","name":"invalid-pattern","expected":"identifier or pattern","found":{"kind":"keyword","text":"open"},"fix":"use a different name like open_","hint":"\nThe left side of a let-expression allows you to pattern match on values to assign them to variables, but also to deconstruct them and access their inner values.\n\n   ```ocaml\n   let variable = 42 in\n   let { x; _ } = point in\n   let Some x = optional in\n   (* ... *)\n   ```\n\nBeware that pattern matching on only one of many possible values will lead to runtime errors!\n"},"span":{"start":18,"end":19}},{"kind":{"id":"E0003","name":"missing-let-binding-equals","expected":"=","found":{"kind":"identifier","text":"M"},"fix":"add = between the pattern and expression","hint":"Every let binding needs an = between the pattern and the expression."},"span":{"start":18,"end":18}}]}
